{
  "texts": [
    "However, the gain compared to well-trained smaller models is not large.WizardLM's performance increases from 53% to 56.4% by increasing the model size from 13B to 30B parameters.",
    "MPT jumps from 40.9% (7B) to 48.2% (30B) accuracy.",
    "Alpaca even drops from 46.4% (7B) to 45.5% (30B).",
    "However, a few other competitive models got available.",
    "Falcon 40B instruct achieved 55.5% accuracy, the same as IBM's Dromedary with 65B parameters and GPTQ [47]."
  ]
}